<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Vaibhav Shukla | UGC & AI Content Creator Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
            animation: pageReveal 1s cubic-bezier(0.1, 1, 0.1, 1) forwards;
        }
        @keyframes pageReveal {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(15px); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }
        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e24 0%, #333138 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 20px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 20px;
        }
        header h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        header h1:hover { animation: textGlow 1.5s infinite ease-in-out; }
        @keyframes textGlow {
            0% { text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 183, 3, 0.2); }
            50% { text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 183, 3, 0.6); }
            100% { text-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(255, 183, 3, 0.2); }
        }
        header p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #ffb703; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .location { font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8; }

        section {
            margin: 40px 0;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            animation: sectionPop 0.8s ease-out both;
        }
        section:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        section:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        section:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        section:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
        section:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }
        @keyframes sectionPop {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.98) translateY(10px); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1) translateY(0); }
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: #1e1e24;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }
        h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background-color: #ffb703;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .card {
            background: #f1f1f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffb703;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) !important;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .card h3 { margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.03) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255, 183, 3, 0.2) !important;
            border-left-color: #fb8500 !important;
        }

        .video-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .video-card {
            background: #e2e2e9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 2px dashed #bbb;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) !important;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .video-card.has-video {
            border: none;
            height: auto;
        }
        .video-card video {
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
            border-radius: 8px;
            max-height: 500px;
        }
        .video-placeholder {
            height: 400px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .video-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.03) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255, 183, 3, 0.2) !important;
            border-color: #ffb703 !important;
        }

        .photo-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .photo-card {
            background: #f1f1f5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275) !important;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .photo-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            display: block;
            background: #ccc;
        }
        .photo-caption { padding: 10px; font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; color: #444; }
        .photo-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.03) !important;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255, 183, 3, 0.2) !important;
            border-color: #ffb703 !important;
        }

        .btn-container { display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 15px; }
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease !important;
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .btn-primary { background-color: #ffb703; color: #1e1e24; }
        .btn-primary:hover { background-color: #fb8500; }
        .btn-secondary { background-color: #1e1e24; color: #fff; }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background-color: #333; }
        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.05); box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); }
        .btn:active { transform: translateY(-1px) scale(1); }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 30px; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #777; }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            section { padding: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Vaibhav Shukla</h1>
            <p>UGC Creator & AI Media Marketing Specialist</p>
            <p class="location">📍 Kanpur, India | Undergraduate Student</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>Hi, my name is Vaibhav Shukla. I am a modern UGC creator who blends authentic video content with <strong>Artificial Intelligence (AI)</strong> and cutting-edge <strong>Media Marketing</strong> strategies to build brand trust.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">I am currently at the beginning of my journey and looking to work with brands to gain real experience in digital content creation. My goal is to create data-driven, highly relatable marketing videos that generate actual conversions and help brands scale online.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="objective">
            <h2>Objective</h2>
            <p>My goal is to partner with forward-thinking brands to deliver high-converting marketing campaigns. I aim to apply advanced AI content workflows and strategic media distribution methods to grow both my skills and the brand's digital presence.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="skills">
            <h2>Skills & Expertise</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>🎬 UGC Video Creation</h3>
                    <p>Producing relatable, high-retention native videos optimized for Reels, YouTube Shorts, and modern ad networks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>🤖 Artificial Intelligence (AI) Production</h3>
                    <p>Using advanced AI models for rapid trend forecasting, script generation, dynamic voiceovers, and automated workflow enhancements.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>📈 Digital & Media Marketing</h3>
                    <p>Understanding viewer psychographics, performance hooks, algorithmic delivery, and strategic content planning to drive organic reach.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>✂️ Video Editing & Post-Production</h3>
                    <p>Crafting engaging, fast-paced sequences with seamless transitions, precise typography overlays, and sound design.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>✍️ Creative Scripting & Storyboarding</h3>
                    <p>Developing persuasive multi-step psychological frameworks to lock down immediate attention within the first 3 critical seconds.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="portfolio">
            <h2>My Work Samples (Videos)</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #666;">Hosted samples of high-impact vertical content and campaign video hooks.</p>

            <div class="video-grid">
                <div class="video-card has-video">
                    <video controls preload="metadata">
                        <source src="videos/sample1.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        Your browser doesn't support video playback.
                    </video>
                </div>
                <div class="video-card">
                    <div class="video-placeholder">
                        <span>Sample Video 2</span>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px;">[Add video here]</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="video-card">
                    <div class="video-placeholder">
                        <span>Sample Video 3</span>
                        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 5px;">[Add video here]</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="aesthetic-photos">
            <h2>Best Aesthetic Captures (Photos)</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #666;">High-quality, eye-catching product imagery and content photography layout.</p>

            <div class="photo-grid">
                <div class="photo-card">
                    <img src="photo1.jpg" alt="Aesthetic Capture 1">
                    <div class="photo-caption">Minimalist Product Shot</div>
                </div>
                <div class="photo-card">
                    <img src="photo2.jpg" alt="Aesthetic Capture 2">
                    <div class="photo-caption">Flatlay Style Media</div>
                </div>
                <div class="photo-card">
                    <img src="photo3.jpg" alt="Aesthetic Capture 3">
                    <div class="photo-caption">Creative Concept Portrait</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="contact">
            <h2>Scale Your Brand Performance</h2>
            <p>I am actively open to collaborations for strategic content consulting, video campaigns, and organic media marketing placements. Let's engineer something viral together.</p>

            <div class="btn-container">
                <a href="mailto:shukla6489@gmail.com" class="btn btn-primary">✉️ Email: shukla6489@gmail.com</a>
                <a href="tel:+918005335295" class="btn btn-secondary">📞 Connect: +91 8005335295</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Vaibhav Shukla. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
